%pyspark

from pyspark.sql.functions import udf

udf_dnt2dt = udf(lambda d, t: d + ' ' + t)

uv = spark.read.parquet("hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/uv.parquet")\
          .withColumn('datetime', udf_dnt2dt('date', 'time'))\
          .drop('date', 'time')\
          .where('date >= "2019-03-01" and date <= "2019-03-04"')
          
uv.show()
uv.createOrReplaceTempView('uv')

%pyspark
from pyspark.sql import Row

chambertemp = sc.textFile("hdfs:///raw/temphumi_1903.csv")\
                .map(lambda s: s.split(","))\
                .map(lambda s: [s[0], float(s[1])])\
                .map(lambda s: Row(datetime=s[0], temp=s[1]))\
                .toDF().distinct().sort('datetime')

chambertemp.show()
chambertemp.createOrReplaceTempView('chambertemp')

%sql
select * from df
where date between '2019-03-01' and '2019-03-04'

paragraphs.title: 2019-03-08 temp
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import FloatType

udf_dt2hm = udf(lambda dt: dt[11:16])
udf_temp = udf(lambda t: float(t), FloatType())

df_temp = spark.read.csv('hdfs:///raw/temphumi_190308.csv')

df_temp = df_temp.withColumn('time', udf_dt2hm('_c0'))\
                 .withColumn('temp', udf_temp('_c1'))\
                 .select('time', 'temp')\
                 .distinct().sort('time')

df_temp.show()

%sql
select time, temp, uvb*100 from temp_uvb
where time > "05:00"
